      {
        "id": "cloud_migration_security",
        "scenario": "A security team overseeing cloud migration. Daily reports:\nIAM policy changes, S3 bucket permissions, CloudTrail\nanomalies, WAF rule triggers, certificate management,\ncontainer vulnerability scans, Kubernetes RBAC audits.\n",
